ITEM 1 72 ADJ1=283 VAL2=2320
EXTEND 1 that leads into The Black Sands
;-------------opening to shop--------
ITEM 2 72 ADJ1=283 VAL2=2321
EXTEND 2 that leads into Momar's Emporium
;--------fountain--------------
ITEM 3 197 ADJ1=178
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
The fountain is large and the water is fresh.
*DESCRIPTION_END
PUT 3 198 VAL2=100 VAL3=0
