NUMBER 2307
NAME Steep Road
DAY_LIGHT 
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
This road winds up the hillside toward the top of the hill toward the tower.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT SE 2306
EXIT N 2310
