NUMBER 2348
NAME Houndsteeth Tower, Dungeon 
DAY_LIGHT 
INDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
A trapdoor leads into this room from the Main Hall above. The room contains
crude shelves and stacks of crates full of supplies, mostly foodstuffs. Drying
onions and other herbs dangle from the floor joists overhead. In the back of
this area is a detention cell. A torch is mounted in an iron bracket on the
wall. An iron door keeps prisoners secure. 
*DESCRIPTION_END
